Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: collective.portlet.itemview
Version: 1.0
Summary: A portlet where you can select one item, and render it with a view
Home-page: http://svn.plone.org/svn/collective/
Author: UNKNOWN
Author-email: jeanmichel.francois@makina-corpus.com
License: GPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        
        This portlet is kind of relation portlet. It display
        a selected item with by default the view @@itemview_portlet.
        
        You can register other views to be used with this add-on
        just by registering a new named utility on the interface
        IPortletView.
        
        
        Changelog
        =========
        
        1.0 (2011-02-08)
        ----------------
        
        - Initial release
        
